    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s seriously like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a scratch or a speck on it! I\u2019ve taken such good care of this beauty, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels and looks brand new, this is the one for you. Come take a look and fall in love!",
