    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54-powered chassis, maintained to an exacting mechanical standard. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a recently overhauled Double VANOS system, ensuring precise valve timing and linear power delivery. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox offers tight, notched engagement, paired with a refreshed factory limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced with structural plates, and the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells\u2014addressing the platform's critical preventative maintenance. The suspension geometry remains true, with all-new polyurethane bushings and factory-spec dampers providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the undercarriage is completely free of fluid seepage or oxidation. This is a turn-key, collector-grade specimen for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
