    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior finish retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of any creases or wear, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and electronic feature operates with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service portfolio with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians. It sits on a fresh set of high-performance tires and features a spotless undercarriage. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for the discerning driver who demands perfection.",
