      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely spotless inside and out! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it still has that fresh feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been kept in truly perfect shape, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
